# TypeScript Standards

Details → [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) (naming, architecture).

- Strict mode in all `tsconfig.json` files
- Import shared types from `@nasa-fuel/shared` — do not redefine message shapes
- `SCREAMING_SNAKE` keys for constant maps (`errors`, `FUEL_FORMULA`); `camelCase` elsewhere
- Business logic pure; side effects only at boundaries (WS handlers, React hooks)

```typescript
// ❌ Side effects in fuel-core
export function calculateAndSend(ws: WebSocket, mass: number): void { ... }
```
